    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail and peel <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>carrot[s] </strong>into a pile of ribbons, then grate the <strong>remaining carrot</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p>",
