    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crack your <strong>egg[s]</strong> into a shallow bowl and beat lightly with a fork</p><p>Add 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span><strong> flour</strong> to a plate and season with<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>, then add your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> to another plate</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper and shred roughly</p>",
      "order": 3,
