    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[450ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and reduce the heat to low</p><p>Add your <strong>soy sauce</strong> and stir through your <strong>mango chutney</strong></p><p>Cook for 5-7 min or until the sauce has thickened to a curry-like consistency</p><p>Season with a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong>, cover with a lid and set aside for later – this is your <strong>katsu sauce</strong></p>",
