    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> and <strong>carrot ribbons</strong> to the bowl with the dressing and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>dressed</strong> <strong>salad</strong></p><p>On a clean board, slice the <strong>breaded</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> finely into strips</p><p>Spoon the <strong>katsu</strong> <strong>sauce</strong> onto the plate and serve the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>breaded</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> over the sauce with the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>rice</strong> and <strong>dressed salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
